e\n- [ ] Add required kubebuilder markers\n\n## Phase 3: Code Generation\n\n- [ ] Run `controller-gen` to generate DeepCopy methods\n- [ ] Verify generated code compiles\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-001/plan.md","time":{"start":1775839185279,"end":1775839185294}}}}
