{"type":"text","timestamp":1775839191900,"sessionID":"ses_287bdc534ffe5Tn3SaX4doioLF","part":{"id":"prt_d78439f92001Go1uK181Ip5FXm","messageID":"msg_d784389ca001P931sHqWP9evz0","sessionID":"ses_287bdc534ffe5Tn3SaX4doioLF","type":"text","text":"Now I have a clear understanding of the requirements. Let me create the delta-spec.md file with GIVEN/WHEN/THEN acceptance scenarios for the AgentRuntime CRD type definition.","time":{"start":1775839191899,"end":1775839191899}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775839241453,"sessionID":"ses_287bdc534ffe5Tn3SaX4doioLF","part":{"id":"prt_d7843a35d001oJaCvn8ThorZW7","messageID":"msg_d784389ca001P931sHqWP9evz0","sessionID":"ses_287bdc534ffe5Tn3SaX4doioLF","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:13","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/delta-spec.md","content":"# Delta Spec: AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime Type Definition\n\n## Overview\n\n**AR ID:** AR-001  \n**Module:** pkg/apis  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Size:** S  \n\nDefine the Go type definitions for the AgentRuntime Custom Resource Definition (CRD) under the API group `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`.\n\n---\n\n## Requirements\n\n### Requirement: AgentRuntime CRD Type Package Structure\n\nThe system SHALL define the AgentRuntime CRD Go types in the package `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` following Kubernetes CRD conventions.\n\n#### Scenario: Package compiles successfully\n- **GIVEN** a clean Go module at repository root\n- **WHEN** the operator runs `go build ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...`\n- **THEN** the package SHALL compile without errors\n\n#### Scenario: Package follows project conventions\n- **GIVEN** the package `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1`\n- **WHEN** inspecting package files\n- **THEN** all files SHALL have consistent package naming, proper doc.go documentation, and follow project conventions\n\n---\n\n### Requirement: AgentRuntime Root Type Definition\n\nThe system SHALL define an `AgentRuntime` struct that implements the `runtime.Object` interface and includes standard Kubernetes metadata, spec, and status fields.\n\n#### Scenario: AgentRuntime implements runtime.Object\n- **GIVEN** the `AgentRuntime` struct defined in `agentruntime_types.go`\n- **WHEN** the code is compiled\n- **THEN** `AgentRuntime` SHALL implement `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object` interface\n\n#### Scenario: AgentRuntime has correct TypeMeta\n- **GIVEN** an `AgentRuntime` instance\n- **WHEN** accessing its `TypeMeta` fields\n- **THEN** `APIVersion` SHALL default to `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` and `Kind` SHALL be `AgentRuntime`\n\n---\n\n### Requirement: AgentRuntimeSpec Definition\n\nThe system SHALL define an `AgentRuntimeSpec` struct with fields for `maxSessionDuration`, `podTemplate`, `sessionTimeout`, and `targetPort` as required fields.\n\n#### Scenario: Required fields are present\n- **GIVEN** the `AgentRuntimeSpec` struct definition\n- **WHEN** inspecting its fields\n- **THEN** it SHALL contain required fields: `maxSessionDuration` (string), `sessionTimeout` (string), `targetPort` (array), and `podTemplate` (PodTemplateSpec)\n\n#### Scenario: JSON tags use camelCase\n- **GIVEN** the `AgentRuntimeSpec` struct with field tags\n- **WHEN** serializing to JSON\n- **THEN** field names SHALL use camelCase (e.g., `maxSessionDuration`, `sessionTimeout`, `targetPort`, `podTemplate`)\n\n#### Scenario: Default values are documented\n- **GIVEN** the `AgentRuntimeSpec` struct with kubebuilder markers\n- **WHEN** inspecting the markers\n- **THEN** `maxSessionDuration` SHALL have default `8h`, and `sessionTimeout` SHALL have default `15m`\n\n---\n\n### Requirement: TargetPort Sub-resource Definition\n\nThe system SHALL define a `TargetPort` struct representing port configuration with `port` and `protocol` as required fields, and optional `name` and `pathPrefix` fields.\n\n#### Scenario: TargetPort has required fields\n- **GIVEN** the `TargetPort` struct definition\n- **WHEN** inspecting its fields\n- **THEN** it SHALL contain required `port` (int) and `protocol` (string) fields with kubebuilder validation\n\n#### Scenario: TargetPort protocol validation\n- **GIVEN** the `TargetPort` struct with kubebuilder markers\n- **WHEN** validating with `protocol: HTTPS`\n- **THEN** it SHALL pass validation (allowed values: HTTP, HTTPS)\n\n---\n\n### Requirement: AgentRuntimeStatus Definition\n\nThe system SHALL define an `AgentRuntimeStatus` struct with conditions and observed state fields.\n\n#### Scenario: Status has conditions\n- **GIVEN** the `AgentRuntimeStatus` struct definition\n- **WHEN** inspecting its fields\n- **THEN** it SHALL contain a `conditions` field of type `[]metav1.Condition`\n\n#### Scenario: Status subresource marker\n- **GIVEN** the `AgentRuntime` struct with kubebuilder markers\n- **WHEN` inspecting the markers\n- **THEN** it SHALL include `// +kubebuilder:subresource:status` marker\n\n---\n\n### Requirement: DeepCopy Methods Generation\n\nThe system SHALL include generated DeepCopy methods for all CRD types to support Kubernetes API machinery.\n\n#### Scenario: DeepCopy methods exist\n- **GIVEN** the generated code from `controller-gen`\n- **WHEN** inspecting `zz_generated.deepcopy.go`\n- **THEN** it SHALL contain `DeepCopyInto`, `DeepCopy`, and `DeepCopyObject` methods for `AgentRuntime`, `AgentRuntimeSpec`, `AgentRuntimeStatus`, and `TargetPort`\n\n---\n\n### Requirement: Scheme Registration\n\nThe system SHALL register AgentRuntime types with the runtime scheme.\n\n#### Scenario: AgentRuntime in scheme\n- **GIVEN** the `register.go` file in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1`\n- **WHEN** inspecting the `AddToScheme` function\n- **THEN** it SHALL register `AgentRuntime` and `AgentRuntimeList` types with the scheme builder\n\n---\n\n### Requirement: Code Generation Integration\n\nThe system SHALL integrate with `controller-gen` for generating DeepCopy methods and CRD manifests.\n\n#### Scenario: Controller-gen generates code\n- **GIVEN** the `Makefile` with `gen-crd` and `generate` targets\n- **WHEN** the operator runs `make generate`\n- **THEN** it SHALL invoke `controller-gen object` to generate DeepCopy methods\n\n---\n\n## File Index\n\n| Path | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go` | AgentRuntime type definitions |\n| `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go` | Scheme registration |\n| `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go` | Package documentation |\n| `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go` | Generated DeepCopy methods |\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1` - Kubernetes metadata types\n- `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime` - Runtime.Object interface\n- `sigs.k8s.io/controller-tools` (controller-gen) - Code generation\n\n---\n\n## Notes\n\n- JSON tags SHALL use camelCase per project conventions\n- Go structs SHALL use PascalCase per Go conventions\n- Kubebuilder markers SHALL follow standard Kubernetes CRD patterns\n- The CRD scope SHALL be `Namespaced` (as per deployment/design.md)\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-001/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/delta-spec.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775839241439,"end":1775839241449}}}}
